e for key industry players at nbc and industrywide top recipients receive an nbc talent holding deal meeting with nbc casting execs and an invitation to join the stand up for diversity college tour diverse staff writer initiative nbc encourages diversity among our writing staffs by funding select staff writer positions open to all scripted nbc primetime series along with some series from our cable networksthese positions are filled with writers selected and hired by the showrunnerproducers of each show along with the guidance of the network and studios late night writers workshop the selected writers will create new sketch material and gain insight into the dynamics of a late night writers room as well as learn about nbcuniversal directing fellowship program the directing fellowship program is designed to take directors accomplished in their respective fields features commercials music videos and give them the opportunity to work alongside episodic television directors  the selected directors will foster relationships and fine tune their art to fit the television format the sundance institute native american and indigenous program the sundance institute native american and indigenous program is a yearround program to deepen the commitment to support native american and indigenous artists and talent this program allows nbcuniversal to build relationships within the native and indigenous communities while creating a pipeline for native actors writers and directors nbcuniversal casting apprentice program an  month rotational program designed for individuals of diverse backgrounds who aspire to join a casting office apprentices are exposed to working in both a network and freelance casting office the apprentices gain exposure to top level programming executives and attend talent showcases comedy clubs and other venues where talent is showcased writers assistant program launched in  nbc entertainment funds a writer’s assistant position on  nbc primetime scripted shows these positions are chosen by the showrunner of the respective show and provide the selected writers the opportunity to be in a television writers’ room and assist in any ways necessary back to top employee resource groups myabilities networkmyabilities network is an employee resource organization built to foster an environment that recruits retains develops and connects the unique skills and attributes of those who have varied abilities httpstwittercommyabilitiesnbcuhttpswwwfacebookcommyabilitiesnetwork asian pacific americans allianceasian pacific americans alliance establishes to attract promote and retain asian and pacific islander american talent within the company  httpstwittercomapanbcuhttpswwwfacebookcomapanbcu black employee networkblack employee network fosters and grows a strong black employee base with focus on contributing their best  both personally and professionally  to the organization and to the community at large httpstwittercombennbcuhttpswwwfacebookcomblackemployeenetwork outout is the lesbian gay bisexual transgender  straight ally employee alliance founded in  we are one of corporate americas oldest lgbt employee groups     httpstwittercomoutnbcuniversalhttpswwwfacebookcomoutnbcuniversal women’s networkthe women’s network fosters professional women development by holding events centered on support of women’s issues key personal development mentoring and educational opportunities   httpstwittercomwomensnetnbcuhttpswwwfacebookcomwomensnetworkatnbcuniversal unidosunidos serves as the premier resource for uniting educating and empowering aspiring and accomplished hispanic professionals   httpstwittercomunidosnbcuhttpswwwfacebookcomunidosatnbcuniversal veterans networkthe veterans network fosters a business culture that recognizes supports develops and promotes the unique characteristics of veterans throughout nbcuniversal  httpstwittercomnbcuvetnethttpswwwfacebookcomnbcuniversalveteransnetwork young professionals networkyoung professionals network y